during fiscal year 2008, we reached a settlement with the internal revenue service (irs) on its
2000-2003 examination.as a result, we reduced our unrecognized tax benefits by $4.8 billion and recognized a tax provision reduction of $1.2 billion.as a result of the 2000-2003 settlement and the related impact on subsequent years, we
