item 8    employee stock purchase plan  we have an employee stock purchase plan for all eligible employees. compensation expense for the
employee stock purchase plan is recognized in accordance with sfas no.123(r). shares of our common stock may be purchased by employees at three-month intervals at 90% of the fair market value on the last day of each three-month period.
employees may purchase shares having a value not exceeding 15% of their gross compensation during an offering period. employees purchased the following shares:
(shares in millions)
year ended june 30,
shares purchased
average price per share
$
20.13
$
26.78
